About

My name is Zanele, born (Bathabile Fortunate Mnguni). I'm a young and creative individual with high interest of digital creativity and arts, born 15 September 1996 in South Africa Pretoria, Matriculated 2015 at Soshanguve Secondary School. I currently reside in Johannesburg. My love and interest of social media marketing started during my first year of college at Boston Media House 2019 as a Media and Journalism student studying to obtain a Diploma in media studies.


When I dropped out during my second year because of financial strain, I decided to offer Social Media Management services as a freelancer with the knowledge I acquired from Marketing, Advertising, PR, and Journalism during my studies, including youtube, reading, google and my personal experience as a Micro-influencer who managed to grow her personal brand on social media. September 2022 I finished a Digital Marketing internship program with Girls in Marketing academy.


I believe in existing with genuine identity, while in volume strive towards the ultimate purpose of attaining the meaning of my potential.





History

Starting my Social Media Management freelancing in 2020 during the covid19 pandemic, I offered my services to a small business brand of a friend and upon management other businesses and personal brands started approaching me because of the quality and value I added to her personal brand and exposure.


I have also outsourced my services to Film and Media organizations and companies, which required me to attend shootings as I was responsible for creating behind the scenes content for their social media platforms. So this adds to my understanding of being able to create content.


Understanding brand strategy and Digital Marketing management, I was able to achieve brand awareness and get successful brand collaborations and campaigns for my clients.


Values

Vision

I am destined to revolve within the digital world. Responsible and accountable for the image in account of my various industry clients, applying relevant attributes to match their demand while creating great reputation.

Mission

While building a retainable and reputable engagement with you and your audience in an uncompromising relationship with your brand, I provide the best service with my professionalism and skills, prioritizing client opinion, while working closely throughout to attain your ideal language, culture and way of conventional life across the board.

Goals

BE THE LEADING SOCIAL MEDIA EXPERT

BOOST BRAND ENGAGEMENT

INCREASE BRAND ENGAGEMENT RATE

ESTABLISH BRAND AWARENESS

GENERATE HIGH-QUALITY LEADS

INCREASE CUSTOMER VALUE
